{"tid":1801520,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果你唔夠膽去和你Shop，但見到手足被咬會好傷心，請你成為一個哨兵","createTime":"2019-12-28T16:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T12:59:30.000Z","uid":179379,"like":98,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"6c776323ecbdeee5fa2b8f0b38be19c148dc14c5","tid":1801520,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"1228德福突然咬咗十幾個<br />\n第一個原因係<span style=\"color: orange;\">大家警覺性仲係好低</span><br />\n另一個就係<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔夠哨兵</span>提供足夠嘅資訊畀佢哋去判斷情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於第一點，請我上一個post<br />\n[溫故知新] 基本戰術及技巧重溫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1797724/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1797724/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個post主要講第二點 - <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>哨兵</strong></span><br />\n依家和你shop都會鳩拉，我知嚇親好多人唔敢出<br />\n但當<span style=\"color: orange;\">現場人數愈少</span>，佢哋嘅處境只會<span style=\"color: orange;\">更加危險</span><br />\n直到<span style=\"color: orange;\">肯行動嘅都拉晒</span>，咁我好肯定<span style=\"color: orange;\">場運動就收皮</span><br />\n但唔敢出嘅你哋其實都可以幫手，就係報哨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>(一) 哨兵種類</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1. 真係路過</span><br />\n可能真係食完飯或者啱啱放工<br />\n見到曱甴<span style=\"color: orange;\">報完哨可以繼續你嘅行程</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2. 定點哨兵 ★</span><br />\n企某個位置<br />\n例如天橋、十字路口、商場或黨鐵出入口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">宜</span><br />\n- 同時食煙 / 講電話 / 打機<br />\n- 隔一段時間就換位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">忌</span><br />\n- 同活動手足有交流<br />\n- 嗌口號<br />\n- 屌狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3. 移動哨兵 ★★</span><br />\n同定點哨兵差唔多<br />\n不過係不斷遊走唔同位置<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">宜</span><br />\n- 周圍望吓舖頭有咩買<br />\n- 根據情況判斷需要哨嘅位置<br />\n- 安全情況下同活動手足報告資訊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">忌</span><br />\n- 喺同一批曱甴面前經過超過2次<br />\n- 眼甘甘望住啲曱甴<br />\n- 同活動手足一齊行<br />\n- 嗌口號<br />\n- 屌狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">4. 跑動型哨兵 ★★★</span><br />\n遊走唔同位置<br />\n有突發情況同資訊要同活動手足報告<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*** 有機會被咬，必須有足夠哨兵經驗 ***</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">宜 / 忌<br />\n- 如果你諗唔到有咩宜同忌，建議你做返定點/移動哨兵先</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(二) 哨兵裝備</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1. 一套適合環境嘅衣著</span><br />\n- 去行街買牛扒，點少得環保袋同冰袋<br />\n- 要返工，恤衫西褲就唔少得<br />\n- 想做運動，梗係一身跑步look啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>*** 唔撚好再著拖鞋，你絕對有可能隨時要跑 ***</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2. 帶多件褸同袋</span><br />\n原理同blackbloc完換衫一樣<br />\n因為哨兵都有可能<span style=\"color: orange;\">被便衣發現/跟蹤</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3. 移動/跑動哨可自己配備可加速嘅工具</span><br />\n- 車<br />\n- 單車<br />\n- 滑板車<br />\n- 風火輪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(三) 報去邊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">地區活動</span>搵返相關嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\">地區哨兵channel</span><br />\n如果係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">大型遊行</span>，或者<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">搵唔到地區哨</span>，就按你個人喜好報 <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">scottscout / hklivemap / 寶寶 / suck 等等</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(四) 報哨格式</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">時間 (24小時制)</span><br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">地點</span><br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">數量</span><br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">狗車類型</span> (可以就有埋車牌) / <span style=\"color: orange;\">曱甴類型</span><br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">行動 / 方向</span><br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">裝備 / 注意事項</span><br />\n<br />\n最重要係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以上嘅嘢一句過，連圖</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n2103 中環碼頭天橋 20綠10速 向IFC推進 有防暴槍/圖盾 已上豬嘴<br />\n1255 銅鑼灣Sogo對出軒尼斯道 2籠3衝 停泊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>*** 報料前請睇清楚有冇重覆 ***</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1. 地點</span><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">商場 / 黨鐵邊層邊個出口</span> (e.g. 新城市地下向大會堂出口)<br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">地標向住邊條街</span> (e.g. 銅鑼灣Sogo對出軒尼斯道)<br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">兩條街交界</span> (e.g. 亞皆老街同彌敦道交界)<br />\n- xx<span style=\"color: orange;\">街</span>同xx<span style=\"color: orange;\">道</span>唔好搞錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2. 狗車類型</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzAXRbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzAXRbw.jpg&h=9209d4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cS3Zj4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcS3Zj4S.jpg&h=8655d583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wP1zTpU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwP1zTpU.jpg&h=1d0df275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbOFOYd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbOFOYd.jpg&h=1d7eb4be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySsfCRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySsfCRy.jpg&h=d444f3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6i45Z4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6i45Z4U.jpg&h=01f3fbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bEqfDc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bEqfDc.jpg&h=e7269763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TOPE4ww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTOPE4ww.jpg&h=39cf4fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3. 曱甴類型</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nSRDAN7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnSRDAN7.jpg&h=f849755f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0ftdzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0ftdzQ.jpg&h=20972f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxoRVOd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxoRVOd.jpg&h=c4b2ab70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vbst8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vbst8f.jpg&h=3b1f7b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NUpd88h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNUpd88h.jpg&h=e2bded8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHHZ4GD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHHZ4GD.jpg&h=ab9786ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gz1TpGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGz1TpGF.jpg&h=15c207ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(五) 注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 因發生多次疑似哨兵被殺事件，最好有<span style=\"color: orange;\">同伴組隊</span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: orange;\">影曱甴時注意自身安全</span><br />\n3. 唔好啩住同frd吹水﹐<span style=\"color: orange;\">時刻留意哨兵channel最新消息</span><br />\n4. <span style=\"color: orange;\">出發前同家人/朋友講聲</span>，完咗記得<span style=\"color: orange;\">報平安</span><br />\n5. 量力而為，<span style=\"color: orange;\">有危險就果斷撤退</span>"},{"pid":"f760cb23a903c39841df155be2ad623f2200908a","tid":1801520,"uid":305536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥) (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801519</a><br />\n<br />\n上水和你shop聽日仲有<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801500</a>"},{"pid":"bb4bfcbe9498e905f12a1496c535d6159a77bf68","tid":1801520,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:46:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1760e474039ebd773bd1cf212f7f373844ebd836","tid":1801520,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和你shop 升級：熱情香港 好客之道 又點少得你！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801116</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dcf0614c3f92b690fed118dce1b07fd1b9462af5","tid":1801520,"uid":202895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"好好嘅資料<br />\nfor新手哨好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e75da9828f14b7699e3a54310477ad4162e5c1","tid":1801520,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"德福本身都勁多便衣狗<br />\n唔關哨事嘛?"},{"pid":"e5f2a663ec59ad06de671a64dbe60ff8