"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3407829dbb937c0d02535e7c3d809b4081472dc","tid":1801520,"uid":179379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"如果你住附近，又唔夠膽去和你Shop，點都會Free咗個人力出嚟<br />\n除非你返屋企有其他戰線打，如果唔係下次全部同我去做哨"},{"pid":"d8d2918320158a21551354fecc4b902291c884ac","tid":1801520,"uid":179379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:03:05.000Z","msg":"唔好落樓哨幾粒鐘都懶<br />\n你可能隨時救返十幾個手足"},{"pid":"773a1c10a3eaf29a010e8769caa7b69bdac0d091","tid":1801520,"uid":115435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"好高質"},{"pid":"313caa61f31e8bcc437617c13155b0f4f5437503","tid":1801520,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ceaf349e1dab1f8cfdc076735d2e70c5f9c569","tid":1801520,"uid":265904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:07:29.000Z","msg":"如果你講今日德福,根本係一個局黎, 唔關哨事啦......"},{"pid":"425d2b759f5504022e3f928c61a2568670cd8208","tid":1801520,"uid":60033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96970a9f581ad0fb8949002dbde37376fac3413c","tid":1801520,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ceaf349e1dab1f8cfdc076735d2e70c5f9c569","tid":1801520,"uid":265904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:07:29.000Z","msg":"如果你講今日德福,根本係一個局黎, 唔關哨事啦......"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"任何和理SHOP, 狗都可以外部大包圍<br />\n可以保護自己既, 就係盡量避免同狗衝突"},{"pid":"f13aaa4766552d09a784aa42c5e2067008c565bd","tid":1801520,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b35bf430649011f3161b007e61e8c37ad204272","tid":1801520,"uid":179379,"like":1,"dislike":0