":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n真係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6196a32f8b738aa366915b20bda882d57a7ff0b","tid":1801520,"uid":283040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"近排啲活動真係少咗好多哨兵"},{"pid":"a04e3878408e869f28040e64e3ebd1fdc60d8f11","tid":1801520,"uid":283040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10e75da9828f14b7699e3a54310477ad4162e5c1","tid":1801520,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"德福本身都勁多便衣狗<br />\n唔關哨事嘛?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"但再上兩次，係無便衣既情況下，啲狗入咗商場企埋係隔離先知。咁樣真係太遲。"},{"pid":"3c3e93aa5a39fabbed7d594b8765f8d0067b9928","tid":1801520,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bca4fb9135b2bf1d8288cbaa5233c387b09923","tid":1801520,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n麻煩唔好懶<br />\n<br />\n點解次次睇直播既人數可以係現場幾十倍<br />\n直播加埋幾萬人，現場就得百幾人<br />\n呢啲情況出現左好多好多次，再係咁落去<br />\n再有心堅持既手足都會比你地搞到心灰意冷<br />\n<br />\n真係唔好懶<br />\n1月1號大遊行我地係咪可以係屋企睇直播唔出去？<br />\n你地都知道應該要出去，點解？<br />\n因為好多人出去，你自己都出去，好驚無人出<br />\n如果1月1出到去得幾百人你會點諗呀？<br />\n咁你地明知要人，點解平時係屋企？<br />\n<br />\n知唔知場運動好易完？有次比班狗咬獲金既<br />\n就又輸唔知幾多手足<br />\n麻煩你地平時都要出席多啲，唔好出賣手足<br />\n要幫手去現場，唔好坐係屋企睇<br />\n之後話好心痛"},{"pid":"821b088bad7e5883e670fff0ed09691b90da0899","tid":1801520,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1039f24bac5cc06de84db67bc6ef7eca7d941741","tid":1801520,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae22c8993477e4c577e873d848acd1242631529","tid":1801520,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=41cda4cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"62b8e555de676d89fd5e9593c831f8c0c2bc8ee0","tid":1801520,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:48:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b973d3987375d3dc836307e8d726760ff3c67ba","tid":1801520,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a322d64527c22beb415ba2ba5abb0297bf0c2343","tid":1801520,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"各Channel 有時又唔識做，未問過就公開哨兵報哨張相，間接公開哨兵身分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呼籲大家報哨前加一句「請不要公開相片」"},{"pid":"e1f0864079e30f3c88a616e78101385accd91bbd","tid":1801520,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a322d64527c22beb415ba2ba5abb0297bf0c2343","tid":1801520,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201